text: Zeinab Suma Jammeh (born ) is the former First Lady of the Gambia and the main wife of the former President of the Gambia, Yahya Jammeh. ==Early life== Zeinab Suma (or Soumah) was born to Alhaji Ibrahima and Rhimou El Hassady Soumah in Morocco. ==References== Category:Living people Category:First Ladies of the Gambia Category:1977 births Category:Moroccan emigrants to the Gambia Category:People from Rabat
title: Zeinab Jammeh
